StringValues.16: A strange old puzzle box. There are two slots, each about the size of a small book, on opposing sides. There is a symbol inscribed on its metal surface; an eight-pointed starburst shape overlaid on a swirling portal. In the heart of the starburst is a crashing wave. Within the folds of the portal swirl are four glass beads, red, blue, violet, and green.
StringValues.14: You have no idea how to use this item.
